title: Massive Addons for WPBakery Page Builder 2.4
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Massive Addons for WPBakery Page Builder WordPress Plugin is the most complete extensions package. Over 1700 presets, more then 70 shortcodes & additions, easy to use. Presets are a unique Massive Addons feature, it allows you to style and change the behavior of your shortcodes with a single click. Preset is a set of shortcode settings it defines each aspect of its look & behavior. MA comes with over 1700 presets, of course you can edit or delete them, on top of that you can easily create your own presets
